---
import Shell from '../components/Shell.astro';
---

<Shell title="Cookie Policy — GEO Optimizer" description="Cookie policy for GEO Optimizer, covering cookie categories, storage inventory, and consent management." canonical="https://geoready.dev/cookie-policy/">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-10 md:py-16">
    <header class="mb-14 md:mb-20">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[10px] font-mono text-text-muted uppercase tracking-wider">
        <span>GEO Optimizer</span>
        <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-text-muted" />
        <span>Cookie Policy</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="mt-3 font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-text-primary leading-tight tracking-tight">Cookie Policy</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-base text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Last updated: May 12, 2026</p>
    </header>

    <div class="space-y-10 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-3">What are cookies and similar technologies</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">
          Cookies are small text files that websites place on your device to store information. We also use similar technologies such as localStorage and sessionStorage to save data in your browser. This Cookie Policy describes what we use, why, and how you can manage your preferences.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-3">Categories of cookies and storage we use</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 mt-4">
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-bg-surface p-4">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-text-primary mb-1">1. Necessary</h3>
            <p class="text-sm">Essential for the site to work correctly. They cannot be disabled and do not require consent. This includes the storage used to remember your cookie preferences so you are not prompted on every visit.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-bg-surface p-4">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-text-primary mb-1">2. Preferences</h3>
            <p class="text-sm">Remember your settings and choices (for example, layout or display preferences) to improve your experience. Disabled by default.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-bg-surface p-4">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-text-primary mb-1">3. Analytics</h3>
            <p class="text-sm">Help us understand how visitors interact with the site by collecting anonymous, aggregated statistical data. We do not use analytics by default and only activate them if you provide explicit consent. Currently, Google Analytics 4 is configured but not loaded unless both a measurement ID is set and you have explicitly accepted analytics.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-bg-surface p-4">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-text-primary mb-1">4. Marketing</h3>
            <p class="text-sm">Used to deliver personalized advertisements and measure campaign performance. At this time, no marketing cookies or trackers are used on this site.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-3">Cookie and storage inventory</h2>
        <p class="mb-4 text-sm">The following table lists every cookie, localStorage item, or external request configured for this site.</p>

        <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-border">
          <table class="w-full text-sm">
            <thead>
              <tr class="bg-bg-subtle text-text-muted text-[11px] font-mono uppercase tracking-wider">
                <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold border-b border-border">Name</th>
                <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold border-b border-border">Category</th>
                <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold border-b border-border">Type</th>
                <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold border-b border-border">Provider</th>
                <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold border-b border-border">Duration</th>
                <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold border-b border-border">Status</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="divide-y divide-border">
              <tr class="bg-bg-surface">
                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-text-primary">geo_cookie_consent</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3"><span class="text-[11px] font-mono font-semibold text-accent-success border border-accent-success/20 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">Necessary</span></td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">localStorage</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">GeoReady</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">6 months</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3"><span class="text-[11px] font-mono text-accent-success font-semibold">Active</span></td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="bg-bg-base">
                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-text-primary">_ga</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3"><span class="text-[11px] font-mono font-semibold text-accent-teal border border-accent-teal/20 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">Analytics</span></td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Cookie</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Google LLC</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">2 years</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3"><span class="text-[11px] font-mono text-text-muted">Not active</span></td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="bg-bg-surface">
                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-text-primary">_ga_&lt;container-id&gt;</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3"><span class="text-[11px] font-mono font-semibold text-accent-teal border border-accent-teal/20 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">Analytics</span></td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Cookie</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">Google LLC</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3">2 years</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3"><span class="text-[11px] font-mono text-text-muted">Not active</span></td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-4 text-xs text-text-muted">
          <p>
            <strong class="text-text-secondary">Fonts:</strong> Fonts are self-hosted and loaded from the same domain. They do not generate requests to external CDNs and do not set cookies.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            <strong class="text-text-secondary">Astro/React framework:</strong> The static frontend does not set framework-specific cookies. No session or tracking cookies are created by Astro, React, or Tailwind CSS.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-3">How to manage or revoke your consent</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">
          You can change your cookie preferences at any time by clicking the floating <strong class="text-text-primary">Cookies</strong> button at the bottom-left of every page.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-3">
          You can also manage cookies directly through your browser settings:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-sm">
          <li><a href="https://support.google.com/chrome/answer/95647" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent-teal hover:underline">Google Chrome</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/cookies-information-websites-store-on-your-computer" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent-teal hover:underline">Mozilla Firefox</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://support.apple.com/en-us/105082" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent-teal hover:underline">Safari</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-edge" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent-teal hover:underline">Microsoft Edge</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-3">Third-party services</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">
          This site does not currently embed third-party advertising or social widgets. If Google Analytics 4 is activated in the future, data will be processed by Google LLC under their privacy policy. You can review it here:
        </p>
        <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent-teal hover:underline">Google Privacy Policy</a>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-3">Privacy policy</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">
          For information about data processing, legal basis, user rights, and contact details, see our <a href="/privacy/" class="text-accent-teal hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-3">Updates to this policy</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">
          We may update this Cookie Policy when we add or remove cookies or storage technologies. If we make material changes, we will prompt you to review your preferences again via the cookie banner.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "WebPage",
    "name": "Cookie Policy — GEO Optimizer",
    "description": "Cookie policy for GEO Optimizer, covering cookie categories, storage inventory, and consent management.",
    "url": "https://geoready.dev/cookie-policy/",
    "isPartOf": {
      "@type": "WebSite",
      "name": "GEO Optimizer",
      "url": "https://geoready.dev"
    }
  })} />
</Shell>